Summary of Position

The Southern Office Recruiter is primarily responsible for driving and managing all aspects of recruiting for Associates, Business Analysts, Summer Associates, and Summer Business Analysts with a focus on the Houston location. The ideal candidate will have McKinsey recruiting experience and will serve as an integral member of both the Southern Office recruiting team and Houston location.

