Willing to contribute to heavy administrative tasks required in all aspects of the candidate management process
Ability to look beyond own responsibilities in order to help team members with more urgent deadlines as needed
4-year college degree required


Mobility
While the role is a Southern Office Recruiter, s/he will reside in Houston and therefore we may offer moderate mobility.

